Class CompactPrintingVisitor

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    TemplateCompactPrintingVisitor
    public class CompactPrintingVisitor
extends DefaultTreeVisitor
    A compact-printer for CssTree instances. TODO(oana): Change this pass to stop visiting when definitions are encountered. The same goes for its test.
